Revamp README with expanded docs, usage, and examples

Completely rewrote and reorganized README.md for clarity and usability. Added detailed project overview, key features, installation and usage instructions, code examples, architecture breakdown, performance benchmarks, and educational value. Improved documentation and contribution guidelines, and introduced new sections for security, acknowledgments, and support. Removed redundant and outdated content for a more streamlined and informative experience.
